Class NotificationPanelBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.faces.component.UIComponent
      • javax.faces.component.UIComponentBase
        • org.icefaces.ace.component.notificationpanel.NotificationPanelBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.EventListener, javax.faces.component.behavior.ClientBehaviorHolder, javax.faces.component.PartialStateHolder, javax.faces.component.StateHolder, javax.faces.component.TransientStateHolder, javax.faces.event.ComponentSystemEventListener, javax.faces.event.FacesListener, javax.faces.event.SystemEventListenerHolder, IceClientBehaviorHolder, INotificationPanel
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NotificationPanel

    public abstract class NotificationPanelBase
extends javax.faces.component.UIComponentBase
implements INotificationPanel, IceClientBehaviorHolder
    The Notification Panel is a component that displays a multipurpose fixed positioned panel for notification. Any group of JSF content can be placed inside notification panel. If position of panel is out of place, try putting it as last child of body.

    For more information, see the NotificationPanel Wiki Documentation.
